desc: Closely resembling ordinary spiders, but with a body the length of a man’s and unnaturally long legs, giant spiders are horrifically mutated versions of their lesser counterparts, swollen to a monstrous size by the forces of Chaos. Their heads are surmounted by up to eight large eyes and an even larger pair of mandibles.

